 syndrome (SARS) or influenza: policy evaluation. BMJ. 331 (7527): 1242-3. 10.1136/bmj.38573.696100.3A. 2005 Nov 26 <span class="nowrap">[<a class="int-reflink" href="/pmc/articles/PMC1289362/">PMC free article</a>]</span> [<a href="/pubmed/16176938" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=1618830&amp;issue-id=354895&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>]</span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR18">18. <span class="element-citation">Cox NJ, Subbarao K. Global epidemiology of influenza: past and present. <span><span class="ref-journal">Annu Rev Med. </span>2000;<span class="ref-vol">51</span>:407\xe2\x80\x9321. doi: 10.1146/annurev.med.51.1.407.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/10774473" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=1618830&amp;issue-id=354895&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] [<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1146%2Fannurev.med.51.1.407" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1618830&amp;issue-id=354895&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">CrossRef</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Annu+Rev+Med&amp;title=Global+epidemiology+of+influenza:+past+and+present&amp;author=NJ+Cox&amp;author=K+Subbarao&amp;volume=51&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;pages=407-21&amp;pmid=10774473&amp;doi=10.1146/annurev.med.51.1.407&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=1618830&amp;issue-id=354895&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="CR19">19. <span class="element-citation">Rvachev LA, Longini IM., Jr A mathematical model for the global spread of Influenza. <span><span class="ref-journal">Mathematical Biosciences. </span>1985;<span class="ref-vol">75</span>:3\xe